---
// Minimal Process Section
---

<section id="process" class="section-padding bg-gray-50">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mb-16 fade-in-up">
      <p class="minimal-subheading mb-4">My Approach</p>
      <h2 class="minimal-heading mb-6">Design Process</h2>
      <p class="minimal-body">
        A systematic approach to solving problems through user-centered design, combining research insights with creative solutions.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Process steps grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <!-- Step 1: Research -->
      <div class="minimal-card fade-in-up delay-100">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-black text-white font-semibold text-lg mb-6">
          01
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Research</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          User interviews, competitive analysis, and data gathering to understand the problem space deeply.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2: Ideation -->
      <div class="minimal-card fade-in-up delay-200">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-black text-white font-semibold text-lg mb-6">
          02
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Ideation</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          User flows, wireframes, and concept exploration to develop potential solutions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3: Prototyping -->
      <div class="minimal-card fade-in-up delay-300">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-black text-white font-semibold text-lg mb-6">
          03
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Prototyping</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          High-fidelity prototypes with refined interactions and visual design systems.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4: Validation -->
      <div class="minimal-card fade-in-up delay-400">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-black text-white font-semibold text-lg mb-6">
          04
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Validation</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          User testing, iteration, and final handoff with comprehensive documentation.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
